description:
Bread with a fluffy texture.
Recovers 300 HP
name: Fluffy Bread

description:
Crispy, toasted bread.
Recovers 600 HP
name: Toasted Bread

description:
Delicious crispy bread with a golden coat.
Recovers 1200 HP
name: Golden Bread

description:
A very nutritious pie, filled with goodness.
Fully recovers HP.
name: Tasty Pie

description:
A tasty piece of cheese.
Recovers 40 MP
name: Mature Cheese

description:
Cheese with a rich, creamy taste.
Recovers 100 MP
name: Creamy Cheese

description:
Delicious cheese with added spice.
Recovers 200 MP
name: Spiced Cheese

description:
A cheese made lovingly over time.
Fully recovers MP
name: Blue Cheese

description:
A fresh tomato grown large in the sun.
Revives a fallen ally with 50% HP.
name: Puffy Tomato

description:
A special tomato filled with an angle's power.
Revives an ally to full health.
name: Angel Tomato

description:
A delicious sandwich made at the Emeralia Inn.
Can be used when a player faints to revive them.
name: Fresh Sandwich

description:
A fruity drinkthat clears the throat.
Removes all negative status.
name: Clearing Drink

description:
Juicy seafood with a satisfying crunchy texture.
Recovers 30% HP, 10% MP.
name: Juicy Seafood

description:
An afro wig brimming with electricity.
When used on an enemy it can paralyze them.
name: Pachi-Pachi Afro

description:
A bright crystal that teleports you to the gallery
room. There you can re-visit tickle scenes.
name: Reflection Crystal

description:
Allows you to teleport to areas previously visited.
Shortcut Key ~ [W]
name: Warp Crystal

description:
Allow you to adjust the tickle scenes in game.
※ You can use it without consuming turns.
name: Tickle Settings

description:
Allows you to view the tutorial.
※ You can use it without consuming turns.
name: Tutorial

description:
You can check the quest you are ordered.
Shortcut Key ~ [Q]
name: Quest Log

description:
A book that recors information of all the demons
you've battled.
name: Demon Guide

description:
A dark jewel that resets your Skill Tree.
All your SP will be refunded.
name: Reset Sphere

description:
Reduces your HP to 0, losing the battle.
※ You can use it without consuming turns.
name: Suicide Bomb

description:
Temporarily increases the chance for rare demon
encounters.
name: Lucky Perfume

description:
A rare special jewel that shines brightly.
Increases the SP of both Haruka and Yuzu by 3.
name: SP Sphere

description:
Quest from Charlotte, the innkeeper.
Collect water from the fountain in the Emerald Forest!
name: Charlotte and the Fountain

description:
Quest received from the Guild.
Get rid of the Warp Moles in Emerald Forest!
name: Mole Extermination!

description:
Quest from Charlotte's mother.
Charlotte needs rescuing from the Emerald Cave!
name: Demonic Kidnapping!

description:
Quest from Aqua
Shrine maiden Elias needs escorting to the Shrine.
name: Offering for the Sea God!

description:
A quest from Aqua.
Find 5 seafood pieces from Echo Shell demons!
name: Shell Hunt

description:
A quest from Elias.
Aqua went to the Sea God shrine alone. Find her!
name: Aqua is Missing!

description:
Quest from El Grande, head knight.
Find the missing knight named Sickle!
name: The Missing Knight

description:
Quest from the knight at the entrance.
Find the Cryolite Ore in the Ice Labyrinth.
name: Barricade Busted

description:
Quest from Elil.
Save Nana from Almegia! She in the laboratory.
name: MG - 007

description:
Quest from Nana.
It's finally time to defeat the Dmon Lord.
name: The Demon Lord

description:
Quest for the Mushroom Maniac.
Collect 5 Jade Mushrooms from the Emerald Forest.
name: Mushrooms for the Maniac

description:
Quest from the adventurer that fell down the Warp
Moles' nest. Bring him a Fresh Sandwich!
name: I need a Fresh Sandwich!

description:
Quest from the lady adventurer from the Guild.
Collect 5 Mudpacks from Mudgrub demons.
name: I want to be beautiful

description:
A quest from a fisherman in Sapphire Village.
Deliver the fish to the merchant in Emeralia.
name: Fish Delivery

description:
A quest from the boy in Sapphire Village.
Find a golden Reverse Shrimp! You only have to see it.
name: The Golden Shrimp

description:
Quest from an Adventurer in Sapphire Village.
Bring them a 'Shell Shield' orb!
name: The Best Defense

description:
Quest for the fashionable girl.
Collect 5 husky furs from Asura Yeti.
name: The Price of Fashion

description:
Quest for an adventurer of Magistia.
Find the rare 'Afro Harpy' demon and report back!
name: Afro of Passion

description:
Quest from a knight at the headquarters.
Collect 1 Clearing Drink, 5 Ice Flowers and 5 Tentacles!
name: Energy Drink!

description:
An empty bottle kept from Charles.
Let's bring water from the fountain and take it home.
name: Empty Bottle

description:
A bottle that gathered the water of the Emeral Fountain.
Let's take it under Charles.
name: Emerald Water

description:
A pot of gunpowder that was hidden inside the cave.
Perhaps you can use it to clear a path?
name: Gunpowder Stash

description:
Fresh Fish caught by the fisheman of Sapphire Village.
Take it to the fish merchant in Emeralia Village!
name: Fresh Fish Package

description:
An assortment of food from Emeralia village.
(Don't eat it Haruka...)
name: Food Platter

description:
Scraps of seafood hoarded by an Echo Shell.
Best not eat it...
name: Seafood Piece

description:
A handy piece of rope, strong enough to support
several people. Perhaps you can use this...
name: Circular Rope

description:
A magical stone that radiates warm energy.
Makes it possible to travel to cold areas.
name: Cairo Stone

description:
Very durable mineral.
It is necessary for repairing the barricade.
name: Cryolite

description:
A device for repairing the entrance of the school.
Let's take it under the ticket.
name: Repair Device

description:
Proof of clearing the Demon Training Ground on Easy
setting. 'Not Bad!'
name: Pot of Blessing

description:
Proof of clearing the Demon Training Ground on Normal
setting. 'Thanks for playing!'
name: Pot of Victory

description:
Proof of clearing the Demon Training Ground on Destroy
setting. Clearly you are the master of this game!
name: Pot of Mastery
